    </tbody>
  </table>
</div>

<h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">Y Tile Strategy</h2>

<div class="not-prose my-6 grid grid-cols-1 gap-4">
  <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-purple-500/30 bg-purple-950/20 hover:border-purple-400 transition-colors">
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-purple-400 font-semibold">Consonant-heavy rack rescue:</span> If you draw 5-6 consonants, Y is your lifeline. GYM, CRY, DRY, FRY, PLY, SKY, WHY — memorise these Y-as-vowel words for emergencies.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-purple-500/30 bg-purple-950/20 hover:border-purple-400 transition-colors">
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-purple-400 font-semibold">-LY suffix extension:</span> Adding -LY to adjectives on the board creates easy bingo candidates — QUICKLY, SHARPLY, DARKLY. Each -LY adds 5 points (L1+Y4) plus the word bonus.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-purple-500/30 bg-purple-950/20 hover:border-purple-400 transition-colors">
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-purple-400 font-semibold">Y hooks everywhere:</span> Many words accept Y as a front or back hook — EARLY from EARL, YEARLY from YEAR. Scan the board for hook opportunities before playing Y elsewhere.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">-LY Suffix Mastery</h2>

<div class="not-prose my-6 p-5 rounded-xl border border-blue-500/30 bg-blue-950/20">
  <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-blue-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">💡 Key Insight</p>
  <p class="text-base text-gray-200">The <span class="text-white font-medium">-LY suffix is Y's bingo factory</span>. Adding -LY to adjectives on the board extends them by 2 tiles while adding L(1)+Y(4)=5 points. QUICK→QUICKLY, DARK→DARKLY, SHARP→SHARPLY — each extension can trigger a bingo if you use all 7 tiles.</p>
</div>

<div class="not-prose my-6 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-3">
  <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">DARKLY</span><span class="text-blue-400 text-xs">14 pts</span></span>
  <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">DRYLY</span><span class="text-blue-400 text-xs">12 pts</span></span>
  <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">SLYLY</span><span class="text-blue-400 text-xs">11 pts</span></span>
